                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010114-17-off90 t18010114-17-cd91"></join>, three pounds thirteen ounces of indigo, value 20s.
            </rs> the property of the 
               <persName id="t18010114-17-victim194" type="victimName">
                     <rs id="t18010114-17-viclabel92" type="occupation">United Company of Merchants trading to the East-Indies</rs>
